arStrings.szText: "I have done all that you asked, Ormus."
You have done much to restore the faith of the people of Nahantu. They still grieve their loss, but it is a wound that may now bleed cleanly... and heal.
Ormus is in your debt, but safeguarding the world from the forces of Hell is a task without end. You well know the challenges before you, and the path to victory.
Ormus trusts you to decide which battles are most in need of your aid. You are now prepared for the torments ahead.
